<doc id="393646" wikidata="Q147036" url="?curid=393646" title="Muhammad az-Zanati">
<text>Muhammad al-Zanati ( ) is a Libyan politician who was the General Secretary of the General People&#x27;s Congress, and the head of state of Libya from 18 January 1992 until 3 March 2008. He was reappointed on 1 March 2000. He is of the Qadhadhfa branch of the Houara tribe.

